@thehowlerusa Thanks for replying.  Not to get too technical, but isolation is for the sick while quarantine actually is for people who may look and feel healthy but be pre-symptomatic or asymptomatic virus spreaders. A big  concern with Covid is that many can spread virus without symptoms.

A common sense reminder- if you got a #coronavirus test due to symptoms or because of an exposure to someone with #COVID19, please self isolate at least until you get your test results back if possible. If you must go out, it‚Äôs especially important to wear a mask and distance. https://t.co/7ODrU9zR6c
